scsi: ufs: Add DELAY_BEFORE_LPM quirk for Micron devices

It is confirmed that Micron device needs DELAY_BEFORE_LPM quirk to have a
delay before VCC is powered off. Sdd Micron vendor ID and this quirk for
Micron devices.

